data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","sequence_number":295,"item_id":"msg_aff21da1efb93693006933c0f03a708190888c509749119910","output_index":1,"content_index":0,"text":"Contoso offers a product under the brand name Contoso Galaxy Innovations, categorized as Smart Eyewear. This product features several advanced technologies, including:\n\n1. **Augmented Reality Interface**: Allows users to experience enhanced reality through the eyewear.\n2. **Voice-Controlled AI Agent**: Facilitates hands-free operation and interaction with the device using voice commands.\n3. **HD Video Recording with 3D Audio**: Provides high-definition video capture capabilities along with immersive 3D sound.\n4. **UV Protection and Blue Light Filtering**: Offers eye protection against harmful UV rays and reduces strain from blue light.\n5. **Wireless Charging with Extended Battery Life**: Features convenient charging methods and prolonged use without frequent recharges.\n\nThe product comes with a user guide covering various aspects:\n\n- **Introduction** to the SmartView Glasses.\n- **Product Overview** of features and controls.\n- **Sizing and Fit** for optimal comfort and style.\n- **Proper Care and Maintenance** procedures.\n- **Break-in Period** to adjust to the augmented reality experience.\n- **Safety Tips** for usage in different environments.\n- **Troubleshooting** guide with solutions for common issues.\n\nAdditionally, it includes a two-year limited warranty on electronic components, contact information for customer support, and a 30-day return policy. Some frequently asked questions cover syncing, connection troubleshooting, and customizing augmented reality environments.","logprobs":[]}

