data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","sequence_number":241,"item_id":"msg_aff21da1efb93693006933c0f5c7608190b8ec3390a3fc9917","output_index":1,"content_index":0,"text":"Smart Eyewear from Contoso Galaxy Innovations offers a range of advanced features, including:\n\n1. **Augmented Reality Interface**: This feature enhances the real-world experience by overlaying digital information onto the physical world, providing a more immersive experience.\n\n2. **Voice-Controlled AI Agent**: Allows users to interact with the device hands-free, using voice commands for various functions.\n\n3. **HD Video Recording with 3D Audio**: Provides high-definition video capture and immersive audio recording, delivering a rich multimedia experience.\n\n4. **UV Protection and Blue Light Filtering**: Offers protection against harmful ultraviolet rays and reduces eye strain caused by blue light exposure.\n\n5. **Wireless Charging with Extended Battery Life**: This feature ensures convenient charging and prolongs usage time without needing frequent recharges.\n\nThe product is supported by a comprehensive user guide, which includes:\n\n- **Product Overview**: Details of features and controls.\n- **Sizing and Fit**: Tips for finding a comfortable and stylish fit.\n- **Proper Care and Maintenance**: Guidelines for cleaning and maintaining the glasses.\n- **Troubleshooting Guide**: Solutions for common issues.","logprobs":[]}

